Name: param_lulc
Description: Table of LULC parameters
Mandatory Fields: Id & Name & Alias & Color & f_cpmax & f_sfmax & f_roots & f_perv & f_iri & f_ira & usle_C & usle_P & load_N & load_P

Name: param_soils
Description: Table of Soils parameters
Mandatory Fields: Id & Name & Alias & Color & f_ksat & f_rho & usle_K

Name: param_hydro
Description: Table of model parameters

Name: map_soils
Description: Map of Soils types

Name: map_lulc
Description: Map of LULC (land use and land cover) classes

Name: map_basin
Description: Basin boolean map

Name: map_twi
Description: Map of the Topographical Wetness Index (TWI)

Name: map_hand
Description: Map of the Height Above Nearest Drainage (HAND)

Name: map_slope
Description: Map of terrain slope

Name: map_ET_obs_Date
Description: Map of observed Evapotranspiration in Date (example: map_ET_obs_2022-01-29)

Name: map_cpmax
Description: Map of `cpmax` parameter spatial factor field

Name: map_sfmax
Description: Map of `sfmax` parameter spatial factor field

Name: map_roots
Description: Map of `roots` parameter spatial factor field

Name: map_perv
Description: Map of `perv` parameter spatial factor field

Name: map_iri
Description: Map of `IRI` input spatial factor field

Name: map_ira
Description: Map of `IRA` input spatial factor field

Name: map_ksat
Description: Map of `ksat` parameter spatial factor field

Name: map_rho
Description: Map of `rho` parameter spatial factor field

Name: series_obs
Description: Time series of observed hydrologic processes
Optional Fields: Q_obs & Flow_obs & ET_obs & f_cpmax_Alias & f_sfmax_Alias & f_roots_Alias

Name: param_shru
Description: Table of SHRU parameters
Mandatory Fields: Id & Name & Alias & f_cpmax & f_sfmax & f_roots & f_perv & usle_C & usle_P & load_N & load_P &  f_ksat & f_rho & usle_K

Name: hist2d_extent
Description: 2-D histogram (counting matrix) of spatial units within the full map extent

Name: hist2d_basin
Description: 2-D histogram (counting matrix) of spatial units within the basin extent

Name: zmap_Var_Date
Description: ZMap of simulated Var in Date (ex: zmap_Inf_2022-02-01)

Name: zmap_Var_Stat
Description: ZMap of the statistics Stat of simulated Var (ex: zmap_Inf_Sum)

Name: zmap_Var_Stat_annual
Description: ZMap of the statistics Stat of simulated Var in annual scale (ex: zmap_Inf_Sum_annual)

Name: map_shru
Description: Map of SHRU (surface hydrologic response units)

Name: map_Var_Date
Description: Map of simulated Var in Date (ex: map_Inf_2022-02-01)

Name: map_Var_Stat
Description: Map of the statistics Stat of simulated Var (ex: map_Inf_Sum)

Name: map_Var_annual_Stat
Description: Map of the statistics Stat of simulated Var in annual scale (ex: map_Inf_Sum_annual)

Name: series_sim
Description: Time series of simulated hydrologic processes
Mandatory Fields: P & T & IRA & IRI & PET & ET & Cp & Sf & D & Vz & Inf & Intc & Ints & TF & R & RIE & RSE & RC & Qv & Qs & Qb & Q & Flow
Optional Fields: Q_obs & Flow_obs & ET_obs & f_cpmax_Alias & f_sfmax_Alias & f_roots_Alias
